org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.syntax

Class BaseToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • Annotation
      • org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.syntax.BaseToken
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContractionToken, NewlineToken, NumToken, PunctuationToken, SymbolToken, WordToken

    public class BaseToken
extends Annotation
    A supertype for tokens subsuming word, punctuation, symbol, newline, contraction, or number. Includes parts of speech, which are grammatical categories, e.g., noun (NN) or preposition (IN) that use Penn Treebank tags with a few additions. Equivalent to cTAKES: edu.mayo.bmi.uima.core.type.BaseToken Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015 XML source: /Users/pei/workspace/apache-ctakes/3.2.2/ctakes-ytex-uima/target/jcasgen/typesystem.xml
